  NOTE TO GITHUB USERS

This repository is no longer being updated on github.com, and will
soon be closed. Please visit the project home page to find a link to
its latest home:

  <http://www.muppetlabs.com/~breadbox/software/boggle.html>



Boggle is a solitaire game, based on the Parker Brothers game, in
which the object is to find as many words as possible within the board
in a given time.

The file INSTALL contains information on building and installing the
program. The man page provides directions on using the program.

This program is free software; it is distributed under the terms of
the GNU General Public License version 2 (or, at your option, any
later version). See COPYING for specifics. Share and enjoy.

